🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept and display addition, subtraction, multiplication and division of two numbers.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE operations(a INT, b INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
BEGIN
    RAISE NOTICE 'Addition = %', a + b;
    RAISE NOTICE 'Subtraction = %', a - b;
    RAISE NOTICE 'Multiplication = %', a * b;

    IF b = 0 THEN
        RAISE NOTICE 'Division by zero not allowed';
    ELSE
        RAISE NOTICE 'Division = %', a / b;
    END IF;
END;
$$;


---

✅ Call

CALL operations(10, 5);


